title: Cozy Island Vol. 1 (Casual, Cozy and Puzzle Game Music)
description: Bring Warmth to Your Game with Cozy Island Vol.1: 15 Loopable, YouTube-Safe Tracks!
longDescription:
Bring ambiance, texture and depth to your game with "Cozy Island Vol. 1,” a music pack designed for cozy, casual, and puzzle games. With 15 loopable tracks, this collection offers over 20 minutes of YouTube-safe, royalty-free music that seamlessly integrates into your game, providing an inviting and immersive experience for players.


Features:


- 15 Loopable Tracks: Enjoy continuous, seamless music loops to keep players engaged and relaxed, or use the tracks as one-off cues for events, items etc! 


- BPM Listed in Titles: Easily create perfect loops in your middleware with BPM listed in each track title.


- High-Quality Audio: All tracks are provided in pristine 24bit/48kHz WAV format.


- Royalty-Free: Use this music without worrying about royalties, safe for YouTube, Twitch and other livestream platforms.



A complete Listen-Only version of the pack can be found here:

https://youtu.be/sE_2IbJDmz8
